{"tid":1893220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抵制TVB週日任】電視悶？有個痴線佬砌咗個 YouTuber 圖書館 (23 Feb)","createTime":"2020-02-23T05:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T23:37:02.000Z","uid":267969,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"ef3d6a8beac25d0f469aafff2fab8b9d6b02918c","tid":1893220,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:52:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>【<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />週日特別任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />23 Feb 2020】</strong></span><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/87145569_575870019936518_3866028164824170496_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_sid=a61e81&amp;_nc_eui2=AeF8EY_mGveLqU30gpF4NDSzZhxDIytiH7f8LeFEjSRNkWTFtt58vIx8q0TMMXphyg9HJ03QVoYDd-DBl5u0F-AwbMIoWnOApsOuyN3WjJPdTA&amp;_nc_ohc=ZD7U8Ra-TCgAX-dU8Cm&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=335804c008b8a020e3cad6cc7ebb05c7&amp;oe=5EBD0931\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F87145569_575870019936518_3866028164824170496_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_sid%3Da61e81%26_nc_eui2%3DAeF8EY_mGveLqU30gpF4NDSzZhxDIytiH7f8LeFEjSRNkWTFtt58vIx8q0TMMXphyg9HJ03QVoYDd-DBl5u0F-AwbMIoWnOApsOuyN3WjJPdTA%26_nc_ohc%3DZD7U8Ra-TCgAX-dU8Cm%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D335804c008b8a020e3cad6cc7ebb05c7%26oe%3D5EBD0931&h=3c32dc2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n週末下午 ViuTV/ 開電視都係重播節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁不如根據個人興趣，支持下本土黃絲YouTuber啦，最緊要戒甩CCTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n認真，唔同TVB或Twitter戰線，你唔跟個人興趣睇YouTube，好難持續嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />註：YouTube下簡稱YT)</span><br />\n <br />\n【STEP2️⃣ 講咗主菜先🍝】<br />\n📌a) Bookmark 痴線佬整嘅「香港YouTuber總錄」<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKTube_Catalog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKTube_Catalog&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAykoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=de488b3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKTube_Catalog</a><br />\n <br />\n✅b) 用星期六日下午，按照個人興趣，訂閱唔同本土YT頻道<br />\n電視悶就睇多啲，記得以下支持YouTuber要點 (credit: 光復YT行動)：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Login 睇, Like, Comment, Share<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇晒, 唔skip, 唔較speed, 音量大於一半<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇完個廣告 OR 睇30秒 OR 同個廣告有互動<br />\n <br />\n(就係呢個痴線佬，認住佢，功德無量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：遊物語 - <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1883949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1883949</a>)"},{"pid":"0ebe8bec3f98402416536de155950c3dccee47b6","tid":1893220,"uid":267969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"【STEP1️⃣ 頭盤🥗】<br />\n👀a) YT戰線101 - 睇晒4條片：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/38Pp455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38Pp455&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAykoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=56d91730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/38Pp455</a><br />\n📌b) 訂閱sayno2tvb YT頻道：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/sayno2tvb_YT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fsayno2tvb_YT&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAykoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=fb403742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/sayno2tvb_YT</a><br />\n(雖然我哋未有YT大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n【STEP 3️⃣ 甜品🧁】<br />\n買Chromecast (非必要，有閒錢先買)，有咗呢個裝置，你可以好方便咁將電腦或電話睇緊嘅YT片射上電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點方便法？自己睇 - <a href=\"https://youtu.be/b04158515vQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb04158515vQ&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAykoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=edd1b557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b04158515vQ</a><br />\n <br />\n💵a) 訂購<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.price.com.hk/product.php?p=364827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fproduct.php%3Fp%3D364827&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAykoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=4baabaea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.price.com.hk/product.php?p=364827</a> 或<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.google.com/hk/product/chromecast?hl=en-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.google.com%2Fhk%2Fproduct%2Fchromecast%3Fhl%3Den-HK&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAykoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=fd09a385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.google.com/hk/product/chromecast?hl=en-HK</a><br />\n <br />\n🗣b) 連登討論：電視睇youtube最平方案 - Chromecast (<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1885437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1885437</a>)"},{"pid":"332aa80b4a1fd365f5967a7aed0c43badfb1ee3c","tid":1893220,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"即時13:00<br />\n全世界入嚟推呢個post上熱門！<br />\n<br />\n(煲大佢!!!) 白領工會有手足因罷工被OK便利店解僱！！嚴正譴責當局無理打壓，製造白色恐佈！！全城追擊OK便利店！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1893153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"30ecad62be5c7251851e17ace30f537074665e54","tid":1893220,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5347604f42c381da5c34cd140ede5655f4f95d0c","tid":1893220,"uid":203710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e116189d22e3ff1a7a1fc65e4e22c23d38696ff","tid":1893220,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef3d6a8beac25d0f469aafff2fab8b9d6b02918c","tid":1893220,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:52:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-s